---
title: Pan-Seared Steaks with Creamy Cauliflower and Garlic Sugar Snap Peas
description: Creamy white cheddar takes cauliflower to new heights in this dish. Served with crispy sugar snap peas and tender steak, this is the perfect dinner for your Valentine!

